    {
      "type": "text", "id": "gr_graph_note", "x": 440, "y": 360, "width": 382, "height": 50,
      "text": "“Is Party A bound by Clause 7?”\n→ 2-hop traversal answers it, with the\n   evidence path attached for review.",
